Whats so hard to understand the difference between <form> and <cfform>? Everything cold fusion related starts with a <cf... <cfif> If you don't like it, you can also use a <cfscript> tag:<p><cfscript>
if(noob)
{
greetings = "Hello Coldfusion N00b";
}
</cfscript><p><cfoutput>#greetings#</cfoutput>
